ygData.messageBody:
You could try low-level aviaks (egrets, darters) and low level centaurs
(foals, shelties) in South K.....plus at night (game night) you pop into
Lake Rathe and can get undead at the gnoll camp.........

From: Curtis Bennett <die_kluge@...>
To: <EQ-Clerics@onelist.com>

Subject: [EQ-Clerics] places to solo
